      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the doctor thing but i really dont have time for appointments right now and i've read a lot of wellness blogs saying that massive doses are fine for a short \"loading phase\" to fix a deficiency. if i'm only doing it for like 10-14 days, the risk of toxicity is basically zero right? it's just a temporary boost.",
