      "content": "wait, you said sunlight is abundant in oslo in the winter?? lol i think you mean the opposite, we barely see the sun here this time of year. anyway, if i'm worried about the calcium thing, can i just take a bunch of extra magnesium and some extra water to balance it out while i'm doing the high vitamin d dose? seems like a logical way to offset the side effects.",
