    "summary": "The user asks about taking extremely high doses of Vitamin D (50,000 IU daily) to boost immunity and attempts to find ways to mitigate the risks of toxicity through magnesium and water. The assistant consistently advises against the high dosage, explains the specific medical risks (hypercalcemia, hyponatremia), and repeatedly refers the user to a healthcare professional.",
